od victims?</strong> <em>If you live in South East Queensland and you have a spare room or even a couch you can help the flood victims</em></span></a></li></ul><ul class="articles"><li class="left"><a href="/blog/ipad-layout-with-landscape-portrait-modes"><span><img src="/img/illustrations/thumb/ipad-layout-with-landscape-portrait-modes.jpg" alt="Free iPad CSS layout with landscape/portrait orientation modes" /> <strong>iPad CSS Layout with landscape / portrait orientation modes</strong> <em>A free iPad optimised website layout that changes design when the device is rotated</em></span></a></li><li class="right"><a href="/blog/css3-starbursts"><span><img src="/img/illustrations/thumb/css3-starbursts.jpg" alt="CSS Starbursts with CSS3 transforms and transitions" /> <strong>CSS3 Starbursts</strong> <em>How to make starbursts without images: a CSS3 tutorial</em></span></a></li></ul><ul class="articles"><li class="left"><a href="/blog/experimenting-with-visited-links"><span><img src="/img/illustrations/thumb/experimenting-with-visited-links.jpg" alt="Experimenting with visited links (the ':visited' CSS pseudo-class)" /> <strong>Experimenting with visited links</strong> <em>A list of neat CSS tricks that make use of visited link styles</em></span></a></li><li class="right"><a href="/blog/inspiration-behind-the-new-look"><span><img src="/img/illustrations/thumb/inspiration-behind-the-new-look.jpg" alt="Design 11: Inspiration behind the new look - website redesign of matthewjamestaylor.com" /> <strong>Design 11: Inspiration behind the new look</strong> <em>A summary of the new design and features of my redesigned website</em></span></a></li></ul><ul class="articles"><li class="left"><a href="/blog/centered-dropdown-menus"><span><img src="/img/illustrations/thumb/centered-dropdown-menus.jpg" alt="Horizontally Centered Drop-Down Menus with Pure CSS" /> <strong>Horizontally Centered Drop-Down Menus</strong> <em>A detailed article explaining how to add drop-down submenus to my 